text: Broken voting machines in Russellville, Ark., tried to automatically tally votes meant for Donald Trump as votes for Joe Biden.
A forensics examination of a Ware County, Ga., Dominion Voting Systems machine found votes were switched from Donald Trump to Joe Biden.
entity_strings: Donald Trump, Joe Biden, Ware County

text: A post shared on Facebook claims over 500,000 votes switched from President Donald Trump to President-elect Joe Biden via voting machine software theft during the 2020 election.
